156
00:08:56,469 --> 00:08:59,131
- Merely sharing a point of interest.
- Great. So now what am I, huh?

157
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:01,765
- The world's largest ball of string?
- Not you, your behavior.

158
00:09:01,841 --> 00:09:04,002
It was a textbook example
of just how helpless...

159
00:09:04,076 --> 00:09:06,442
we higher primates can be
to our biological urges.

160
00:09:06,512 --> 00:09:10,073
- I am not helpless.
- [Sighs]

161
00:09:10,149 --> 00:09:12,811
- He's not elderly.
- I can control my, uh...

162
00:09:12,885 --> 00:09:14,819
